==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cinque Ports
<hw>Cinque" Ports`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[<ets>Cinque</ets> +
<ets>port</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Eng. Hist.)</fld> <def>Five English ports,
to which peculiar privileges were anciently accorded; -- viz., Hastings,
Romney, Hythe, Dover, and Sandwich; afterwards increased by the addition
of Winchelsea, Rye, and some minor places.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Baron of the Cinque Ports</b></col>. <cd>See under
<er>Baron</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cinque-spotted</ent>⟦br⟧
